{"tid":2106062,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[唯一取勝法] 李予信：冀同鄺俊宇比拼舞藝","createTime":"2020-07-13T05:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T11:03:11.000Z","uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d550d052f6deba8348d1d53116b841aeed8184d","tid":2106062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xwvsFHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxwvsFHM.jpg&h=6c772905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李予信：冀同鄺俊宇比拼舞藝<br />\n李予信外表俊朗，他稱有人覺得他的外貌與藝人余文樂相似，不過他坦言不喜歡這個稱號。李予信亦愛跳街舞，學習街舞已10年的李去年底更在中大校内跳舞比賽奪冠。被問到對民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇10多年前跳街舞的片段有何評價，他直言要在10多年前要學習街舞渠道很少，自學的話只能購買錄影帶，故認為「鄺神」的舞藝已算不俗，又笑言希望與鄺比拼一番。"},{"pid":"b99f7fa5658aba013811d5da34ba9e6076d219a1","tid":2106062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"李予信<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DxhNFWsRREw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDxhNFWsRREw&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=23e41e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DxhNFWsRREw</a><br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇<br />\n唔使貼啦"},{"pid":"3bfe8e0f66ab12fea5539434f9e3e55b818477ae","tid":2106062,"uid":204985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%AE%B9%E6%B5%B7%E6%81%A9%E7%B1%8C%E5%82%99%E5%80%8B%E5%94%B1%E8%AC%9D%E7%A5%A8-%E6%8C%87%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E8%AD%98%E8%B7%B3%E8%88%9E%E6%9C%9B%E4%BB%A5%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2581%25A9%25E7%25B1%258C%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2594%25B1%25E8%25AC%259D%25E7%25A5%25A8-%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E8%25AD%2598%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E8%2588%259E%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E